Flying, ward {1}
When Lingering Fear enters the battlefield, mill three cards.
Lingering Fear's power and toughness are each equal to the total number of instant and sorcery cards you own in exile and in your graveyard.

Equipped creature gets +1/+3 and has hexproof from white and from blue.
Whenever equipped creature blocks or becomes blocked, put a +1/+1 counter on it. Until the end of your next turn, it gains double strike and “Whenever this creature deals combat damage to a player, draw a card.”
